msgid "# LMCache-Ascend Deployment Guide"
msgstr "# LMCache-Ascend 部署指南"

msgid "## Overview"
msgstr "## 概述"

msgid ""
"LMCache-Ascend is a community maintained plugin for running LMCache on the "
"Ascend NPU."
msgstr "LMCache-Ascend 是一个社区维护的插件，用于在昇腾NPU上运行LMCache。"

msgid ""
"We provide a simple deployment guide here. For further info about deployment"
" notes, please refer to [LMCache-Ascend "
"doc](https://github.com/LMCache/LMCache-Ascend/blob/main/README.md)"
msgstr ""
"我们在此提供简单的部署指南。关于部署说明的更多信息，请参考 [LMCache-Ascend "
"文档](https://github.com/LMCache/LMCache-Ascend/blob/main/README.md)"

msgid "## Getting Started"
msgstr "## 快速开始"

msgid "### Clone LMCache-Ascend Repo"
msgstr "### 克隆 LMCache-Ascend 仓库"

msgid ""
"Our repo contains a kvcache ops submodule for ease of maintenance, therefore"
" we recommend cloning the repo with submodules."
msgstr "我们的仓库包含一个 kvcache ops 子模块以便于维护，因此建议使用子模块方式克隆仓库。"

msgid "### Docker"
msgstr "### Docker"

msgid "Once that is built, run it with the following cmd"
msgstr "构建完成后，使用以下命令运行"

msgid "### Manual Installation"
msgstr "### 手动安装"

msgid ""
"Assuming your working directory is ```/workspace``` and vllm/vllm-ascend "
"have already been installed."
msgstr "假设您的工作目录为 ```/workspace```，并且已安装 vllm/vllm-ascend。"

msgid "1. Install LMCache Repo"
msgstr "1. 安装 LMCache 仓库"

msgid "2. Install LMCache-Ascend Repo"
msgstr "2. 安装 LMCache-Ascend 仓库"

msgid "### Usage"
msgstr "### 使用方法"

msgid ""
"We introduce a dynamic KVConnector via LMCacheAscendConnectorV1Dynamic, "
"therefore LMCache-Ascend Connector can be used via the kv transfer config in"
" the two following setting."
msgstr ""
"我们通过 LMCacheAscendConnectorV1Dynamic 引入了动态 KVConnector，因此 LMCache-Ascend "
"Connector 可通过以下两种设置中的 kv transfer 配置使用。"

msgid "#### Online serving"
msgstr "#### 在线服务"

